AGRICULTURE CODE

which the commodity is produced and the owner's tenant or
sharecropper.
(7) "Person" means an individual, firm, corporation,
association, or any other business unit.
(8) "Secretary-treasurer" means the secretary-treasurer of
a board.
Acts 1981, 67th Leg., p. 1082, ch. 388, Sec. 1, eff. Sept. 1, 1981.
